                <h1>Understanding Homelessness: Stories, Causes, and Solutions</h1>
                <p>Homelessness is a complex issue affecting millions globally, driven by various factors like poverty, mental illness, and lack of affordable housing. Articles on homelessness highlight personal stories, examine systemic causes, and explore solutions. They aim to raise awareness and advocate for policies that support vulnerable populations.</p>
